description: Try our easy to follow Dill & Mustard Baked Salmon recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Dill & Mustard Baked Salmon Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place a double thickness of greaseproof paper over the dish of salmon and put the pastry squares on the paper. Bake for 10-15 minutes until the pastry is risen and golden. Slide the pastry squares on to the salmon and serve with a herb salad.
